sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant P as Panel/Popup
  participant B as SW
  participant C as Content Script
  participant O as Offscreen Doc
  participant T as Active Tab
  participant D as Downloads

  U->>P: Click Export Full Page
  P->>B: RunFullPageExport
  B->>C: CollectPageArtifacts
  C-->>B: {html, css, js, meta}
  B->>O: ensureOffscreen + init canvas (W x H)
  loop for y in 0..pageH step viewportH
    B->>C: BeginScrollCapture(y)
    C-->>B: {actualY, dpr}
    Note over B: wait CAPTURE_GAP_MS
    B->>T: chrome.tabs.captureVisibleTab
    T-->>B: dataUrl
    B->>O: OffscreenAddFrame(dataUrl, 0, actualY*dpr)
    O-->>B: {framesPlaced}
  end
  B->>O: OffscreenStitchFinish
  O-->>B: {blobUrl, w, h, bytes}
  B->>C: RestoreAfterCapture
  B->>B: JSZip.assemble (page.html + styles.css + scripts.js + screenshot.png + manifest.json + README.txt)
  B->>D: chrome.downloads.download(zipBlobUrl, filename)
  D-->>B: downloadId
  B-->>P: StatusUpdate(Success, filename)
